# graphify ignore patterns (gitignore syntax, last-match-wins).
#
# Minified SilverBullet plug bundles are single-line transpiled blobs that
# graphify's AST extractor mis-parses into a god-node: silverbullet-pdf.plug.js
# (2.5 MB) alone produced ~900 edges and dominated god_nodes, drowning the real
# code abstractions in both the per-repo graph and the unified global graph.
# These are vendored build artifacts, not source, so exclude them everywhere.
*.plug.js
